strategy: This matchup is pretty hard. Don't walk up near your minions or he will E and stun you and out-trade you. He out sustains you as well because of his passive. Save your E to dodge his W. He just stat checks you all game, so you'll probably never win 1v1 unless you outplay him.
tips: Dzukill: level 1 Q poke from wave to force the E, take early bad trade to make sure the wave pushes into you, so you can farm under turret
